OL,3,CPride of Britain: Regional Fundraiser
OL,4,Cof the Year Finalist Steve Jack
OL,6,FBorn with spina bifida, Steve has been
OL,7,Fin a wheelchair since birth. In 2009,
OL,8,Fan infection that led to sepsis meant
OL,9,Fhe had to have one leg amputated to
OL,10,Fsave his life. Three years later, he
OL,11,Fcame into hospital for a routine
OL,12,Foperation and suffered a major bleed.
OL,14,FThis would lead to an amputation of
OL,15,Fhis remaining leg. Steve told us: 'The
OL,16,Fdoctor came in, took the tubes out and
OL,17,Fjust straight away he just said: "do
OL,18,Fyou know what happened?"
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
