OL,3,CPride of Britain: Regional Fundraiser
OL,4,Cof the Year Finalist Steve Jack
OL,6,F'And that's when he just said it. Just
OL,7,Fas blunt as anything, as blunt as you
OL,8,Fcan be. He just said: Your other leg's
OL,9,Fgone."
OL,11,FWhen in rehab from his operation,
OL,12,FSteve heard about a local boy named
OL,13,FJoshua who needed specialist equipment
OL,14,Fto help live with cerebral palsy.
OL,15,FSteve set his sights on the fells,
OL,16,Fclimbing to the top of Latrigg above
OL,17,FKeswick, raising #2000 to help Joshua
OL,18,Ftowards a more active childhood.
