OL,3,CPride of Britain: Regional Fundraiser
OL,4,Cof the Year Finalist Steve Jack
OL,6,FJoshua told us: "I am incredibly
OL,7,Fgrateful for Steve for wanting to help
OL,8,Fme, even though we had never even met.
OL,9,FThe money Steve raised went towards an
OL,10,Foff-road wheelchair which has changed
OL,11,Fmy life.
OL,13,F"I can now go places like across the
OL,14,Fpark, along the beach and in the woods
OL,15,Findependently and enjoy the outdoors
OL,16,Fwith my friends."
