OL,3,CPride of Britain: Regional Fundraiser
OL,4,Cof the Year Finalist Steve Jack
OL,6,FEarlier this year, Steve heard about
OL,7,Fanother local child, three-year-old
OL,8,FKoda being treated for Leukaemia. Once
OL,9,Fagain, Steve hit the gym with a goal
OL,10,Fin mind, becoming the first wheelchair
OL,11,Fuser to complete the Cross Border 10K
OL,12,Frace, raising more than #2800 for
OL,13,FKoda's family.
