OL,3,CPride of Britain: Regional Fundraiser
OL,4,Cof the Year Finalist Steve Jack
OL,6,FLauren Weldon, Koda's mum said: "It's
OL,7,Fbeen nice just to know it's there. And
OL,8,Fhe's to get him a little bits to get
OL,9,Fhim through the day. We bought a
OL,10,Fpaddling pool. As soon as he got his
OL,11,Fline taken out, he was out in the
OL,12,Fpaddling pool. And he's very excited
OL,13,Fto see Mickey Mouse. He's got that all
OL,14,Fplanned out."
