OL,3,CPride of Britain: Regional Fundraiser
OL,4,Cof the Year Finalist Steve Jack
OL,6,FSteve said: "I can't give anything
OL,7,Fback to the doctors and nurses who
OL,8,Fsaved my life. So it's just a way of
OL,9,Fgiving back. If I can help somebody.
OL,10,FHelp that kid in need. If I can do
OL,11,Fsomething to help them. I'll try my
OL,12,Fbest to do it."
